quran[10]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,118,"Sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, ṣàforíjìn, kí O sì kẹ́ (mi). Ìwọ sì l’óore jùlọ nínú àwọn aláàánú.”1 {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ āyah 14.]
  25,64,"(Àwọn ni) àwọn tó ń lo òru wọn ní ìforíkanlẹ̀ àti ní ìdúró-kírun fún Olúwa wọn."
  25,65,"(Àwọn ni) àwọn tó ń sọ pé: “Olúwa wa, gbé ìyà iná Jahanamọ kúrò fún wa. Dájúdájú ìyà rẹ̀ jẹ́ ìyà àìnípẹ̀kun."
  25,66,"Dájúdájú ó burú ní ibùgbé àti ibùdúró."
  26,37,"(pé) kí gbogbo onímọ̀ nípa idán pípa wá bá ọ.”"
  26,38,"Wọ́n sì kó àwọn òpìdán jọ ní àsìkò tí wọ́n fi àdéhùn sí ní ọjọ́ tí (gbogbo ìlú) ti mọ̀."
  26,39,"Wọ́n sì wí fún àwọn ènìyàn pé: “Ṣé ẹ̀yin máa kó jọ (síbẹ̀) bí?"
  27,10,"Ju ọ̀pá rẹ sílẹ̀. (Ó sì ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀.) Àmọ́ nígbà tí ó rí i tó ń mira bí ẹni pé ejò ni, Mūsā pẹ̀yìndà, ó ń sá lọ. Kò sì padà sẹ́yìn. (Allāhu sọ pé:) Mūsā, má ṣe páyà. Dájúdájú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ kì í páyà lọ́dọ̀ Mi."
  27,11,"Àyàfi ẹni tí ó bá ṣàbòsí,lẹ́yìn náà tí ó yí i padà sí rere lẹ́yìn aburú. Dájúdájú Èmi ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run. {1}",1:[Kíyè sí i, àwọn ènìyàn tí kì í ṣe àwọn Ànábì àti Òjísẹ́ Allāhu - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá wọn - ni gbólóhùn " Àyàfi ẹni tí ó bá ṣàbòsí" ń tọ́ka sí. Ànábì Mūsā - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - kì í ṣe alábòsí. Kò sì sí Ànábì kan tó jẹ́ alábòsí nítorí pé, Allāhu - tó ga jùlọ - kì í fi iṣẹ́ ìmísí rán alábòsí. Èyí wà ní ìbámu sí sūrah al-Baƙọrah; 2:124.]
  27,12,"Ti ọwọ́ rẹ bọ igbá-àyà ẹ̀wù rẹ. Ó sì máa jáde ní funfun, tí kì í ṣe ti aburú. (Èyí wà) nínú àwọn àmì mẹ́sàn-án (tí o máa mú lọ) bá Fir‘aon àti àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀. Dájúdájú wọ́n jẹ́ ìjọ òbìlẹ̀jẹ́."